oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Unidentified Recording of Hank Snow #2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features ten songs recorded by Hank Snow. The first two songs, "Lazy Bones" and "Old Doc Brown" include spoken sections. The other nine are non-lyrical versions of the songs. The song "Echoing Guitars" is listed on the box but is not included on this recording. The tape is undated. This tape is forty-two of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow;
